# ===========================================
# SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
# ===========================================

# 1. STRIPE SETUP (Required for payments)
#    - Sign up at https://stripe.com
#    - Get API keys from Dashboard > Developers > API keys
#    - Set up webhooks for /v1/stripe/webhook endpoint
#    - Required events: payment_intent.succeeded, payment_intent.payment_failed

# 2. JAMAICAN BANKING (Production only)
#    - Contact NCB, Scotiabank, LYNK for API access
#    - These require business banking relationships
#    - Development: Use Stripe for testing

# 3. KYC SERVICES (Production only)
#    - TAJ: Apply for API access at taj.gov.jm
#    - Veriff: Sign up at veriff.com for document verification
#    - Creditinfo: Contact creditinfo.com.jm for credit bureau access

# 4. REGULATORY COMPLIANCE (Production only)
#    - BOJ: Register as financial institution at boj.org.jm
#    - NHT: Register as employer at nht.gov.jm
#    - Required for operating financial services in Jamaica

# 5. COMMUNICATION SERVICES
#    - WhatsApp: Apply for WhatsApp Business API at business.whatsapp.com
#    - Twilio: Sign up at twilio.com for SMS services
#    - SendGrid: Sign up at sendgrid.com for email services

# ===========================================
# DEVELOPMENT NOTES
# ===========================================

# For Development:
# - Use only Stripe (payment processing)
# - Use only email notifications (SendGrid)
# - Other services return mock data when credentials are missing

# For Production:
# - All services required for Jamaica compliance
# - Obtain proper licenses and registrations
# - Configure all API credentials

